{
  "bookId": "heshanggong-laozi",
  "num": 41,
  "title": "第四十一章（同異）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "上士聞道，勤而行之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "中士聞道，若存若亡。"
    },
    {
      "text": "下士聞道，大笑之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "不笑不足以為道。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故建言有之："
    },
    {
      "text": "明道若昧，"
    },
    {
      "text": "進道若退，"
    },
    {
      "text": "夷道若纇。"
    },
    {
      "text": "上德若谷，"
    },
    {
      "text": "大白若辱，"
    },
    {
      "text": "廣德若不足，"
    },
    {
      "text": "建德若偷，"
    },
    {
      "text": "質真若渝，"
    },
    {
      "text": "大方無隅，"
    },
    {
      "text": "大器晚成，"
    },
    {
      "text": "大音希聲，"
    },
    {
      "text": "大象無形，"
    },
    {
      "text": "道隱無名。"
    },
    {
      "text": "夫惟道，善貸且成。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上士聞道，自勤苦竭力而行之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "中士聞道，治身以長存，治國以太平，欣然而存之，退見財色榮譽，惑於情欲，而復亡之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "下士貪狠多欲，見道柔弱，謂之恐懼，見道質樸，謂之鄙陋，故大笑之。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不為下士所笑，不足以名為道。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "建，設也。設言以有道，當如下句。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "明道之人，若闇昧無所見。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "進取道者，若退不及。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-8",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 7,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夷，平也。大道之人不自別殊，若多比類也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-9",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 8,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "上德之人若深谷，不恥垢濁也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-10",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 9,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大潔白之人若汙辱，不自彰顯。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-11",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 10,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 6
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "德行廣大之人，若愚頑不足也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-12",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 11,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "建設道德之人，若可偷引使空虛也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-13",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 12,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "質樸之人，若五色有渝淺不明也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-14",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 13,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大方正之人，無委屈廉隅。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-15",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 14,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大器之人，若九鼎瑚璉，不可卒成也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-16",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 15,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大音猶雷霆待時而動，喻當愛氣希言也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-17",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 16,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "大法象之人，質樸無形容。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-18",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 17,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道潛隱，使人無能指名也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-19",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 18,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 9
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "成，就也。言道善稟貸人精氣，且成就之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
